name: SWORD IS AN "S" WORD.
description: Sword is indeed an "S" word. It's also the word itself. Sword / "S" word. One of those rare meta moments in the English language again, where the word itself references itself within the word itself. God I love how wonderfully strange English is. Again, not making this up, just things I discover or think about. I'm sure some of these have been thought up or about as well at some point, but no one has made art about them...as far as I know. I feel it's time for the sheer beauty of the language to shine through.
